<p>
  <ol>
    <li> Monica and Joey were originally supposed to be together but their on set chemistry changed during the show.</li>
<li> They were the first tv cast to negotiate their pay as a group and refused to work unless they all had an equal salary. </li>
<li> The show was originally called 'Insomnia Cafe'.</li>
<li> The names of all 6 main characters were inspired by charcaters from 'all my children'.</li>
<li> Bruce Willis guest starred on the show for free after losing a bet with Mathew Perry!</li>
</ol>
